      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING ADMIRAL (1) has an excellent record over this journey having never missed the placings in seven starts, including four wins and three placings. Was out of placings last time (23.19) at this track in a Grade 4/5, finishing fourth and beaten 5.5 lengths. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. TERESA'S ANGEL (2) had a tough draw to overcome and was game in defeat when only half a length from Silvertree Brad in third (18.62) at this track. Expected to be in the finish again. SURPRISE CHARGE (4) was well back throughout but attacked the line to hit the frame when a 3.5 lengths second (18.91) at this track in Grade 5. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to his name from three starts. Expected to feature again. BEST OF SALLY (8) placed last start and is in the mix again.",
